[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0856","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0856.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0586","title":"多厂商 Host Service Port Handler 组件提权漏洞","description":"网络服务运行在非标准端口上可能导致安全隐患，攻击者可能利用该服务绕过防火墙规则和入侵检测系统，进行未授权访问或权限提升。服务端口隐藏可被用作后门或持久化手段，增加安全监控和审计的难度。该漏洞影响使用非标准端口运行网络服务的系统，需通过端口扫描和基线核查进行检测。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0586"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.060","remediation":"建立并维护全网资产清单，使用 Nmap 等工具定期扫描所有端口，识别运行在非标准端口的服务。对每项服务核实其业务必要性，记录责任人及用途；未经授权的服务立即停止并移除。在防火墙上配置零信任策略，只放行必要端口并对源 IP 做白名单限制。对必须使用非标准端口的服务，确保其本身经过安全加固并定期审计日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0586","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0586.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0586.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0586","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0586.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0586.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0586.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0586.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86247/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0856.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0855","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0855.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1008","title":"xsoldier 0.96 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"xsoldier 0.96 版本程序在处理命令行参数时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 xsoldier 程序传递超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址从而劫持程序执行流，成功利用后可获取受影响系统（RedHat 6.2）的 root 权限。该漏洞利用条件为攻击者需拥有本地系统账户，无需其他特殊权限即可实施提权攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1008"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.753","remediation":"升级 xsoldier 至 0.98 及以上版本，或移除 xsoldier 的 setuid 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/xsoldier）以防止本地提权。如无需该游戏，直接通过 rpm -e xsoldier 卸载。建议升级操作系统至受支持的 Red Hat 或 RHEL 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=freebsd-security&m=94531826621620&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/871","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/229","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1008","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1008.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6ww3-wprw-46qp/GHSA-6ww3-wprw-46qp.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0855.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0854","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0854.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1007","title":"VDO VDOLive Player 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"VDO Live Player 3.0.2 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向用户发送特制的 .vdo 文件触发该漏洞，导致在受害者客户端上执行任意命令。攻击者只需诱导用户打开恶意构造的 .vdo 媒体文件即可完成利用，无需身份认证，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1007"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.627","remediation":"VDOLive Player 3.0.2 已停止维护且无官方安全补丁，建议立即卸载该软件，改用 VLC、Windows Media Player 等仍在受支持的媒体播放器。如需继续使用，可通过防火墙和组策略限制该程序对网络资源的访问权限，并避免打开来源不明的 .vdo 文件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94512259331599&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/872","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19678","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1007","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1007.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65cv-6848-4j95/GHSA-65cv-6848-4j95.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0854.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0853","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0853.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0584","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 文件系统非 NTFS 安全漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统未使用具备访问控制列表（ACL）机制的 NTFS 文件系统，而是采用 FAT16/FAT32 等不支持文件级权限控制的文件系统格式，导致任意本地用户均可绕过权限检查直接读取、修改或删除系统中的敏感文件。由于缺乏文件系统级别的安全隔离机制，攻击者可利用此缺陷实现权限提升或敏感信息泄露，严重影响系统机密性与完整性。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0584"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.830","remediation":"立即将 Windows NT 系统所在分区的文件系统由 FAT/FAT32 转换为 NTFS（通过 `convert c: /fs:ntfs` 命令完成，无损转换）。NTFS 提供文件级 ACL 权限控制，可防止未授权访问。Windows NT 产品已停止支持，强烈建议升级至 Windows Server 2016/2019/2022 或 Windows 10/11 等受支持版本以获取持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/195","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0584.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0584","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0584.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0584.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0584.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x554-2vfc-2px3/GHSA-x554-2vfc-2px3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0584.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86241/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0853.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0852","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0852.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1006","title":"Novell GroupWise Web服务器路径遍历漏洞","description":"Novell Groupwise 的 Web 服务器组件 GWWEB.EXE 存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HELP 参数提交特制的路径遍历请求，导致服务器返回文件系统路径信息，从而泄露 Web 服务器的真实安装目录路径。该漏洞可被用于后续攻击步骤的信息收集阶段，帮助攻击者进一步探测目标系统，扩大攻击面。受影响版本为 Novell Groupwise 5.5 及可能更早版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1006"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.503","remediation":"升级 Novell GroupWise 至 6.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复 GWWEB.EXE 路径泄露问题。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中移除或禁用 GWWEB.EXE 的 CGI 映射，并限制对 /cgi-bin/GW5/GWWEB.EXE 的访问权限以降低暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94571433731824&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob