026-06-16T21:49:30.380","remediation":"升级 Novell GroupWise 至 5.5 Enhancement Pack 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。临时缓解措施：在 Web 服务器（如 Apache 或 Netscape Enterprise Server）上通过 ACL 限制对 GWWEB.EXE 的访问，或删除该 CGI 文件。若无需 Web 邮件功能，建议禁用整个 CGI-BIN/GW5 目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94571433731824&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/3413","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/879","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19682","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1005.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1005","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1005.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1005.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1005.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wjwc-hc6j-xvf2/GHSA-wjwc-hc6j-xvf2.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/LubyRuffy/plugins/blob/f873b19f27c95eaf2993ca4acde5cb7965d2ee3f/pre2008/groupwise_web_interface_help_hole.nasl","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1005.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0850.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0849","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0849.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0582","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 账户锁定策略安全配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统的账户锁定策略存在安全配置缺陷，默认或不当的锁定阈值、锁定持续时间和重置时间设置使得攻击者可对用户账户实施暴力破解攻击。由于缺乏足够的登录失败锁定保护，远程攻击者能够通过自动化工具反复尝试密码，直至获得有效凭证，进而获取系统未授权访问权限，影响系统机密性和完整性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0582"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.593","remediation":"在 Windows NT/2000 的本地安全策略中，将\"账户锁定阈值\"设为 5 次无效登录，\"账户锁定时间\"设为 30 分钟，\"重置账户锁定计数器\"设为 30 分钟。通过「管理工具→本地安全策略→账户策略→账户锁定策略」进行配置，或使用组策略进行域范围下发。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0582","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0582.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0582","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0582.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000134.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0849.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0848","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0848.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0581","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表权限配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的 HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT 注册表项存在权限配置不当漏洞，系统关键权限设置不合理，授予了非授权用户过高的访问级别。本地攻击者可利用该缺陷修改系统文件关联或执行配置篡改，进而实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 全系列版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0581"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.473","remediation":"使用 regedt32 修改 HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT 权限，将 Everyone 组的权限从「完全控制」降为「读取」，移除不必要的用户和组。安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全更新以限制关键注册表项的默认访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0581","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0581.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0581","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0581.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86236/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0848.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0847","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0847.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1004","title":"Symantec Norton AntiVirus NAV2000 POProxy POP服务器缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Norton AntiVirus 2000 (NAV2000) 附带的 POP3 代理服务器 POProxy 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 POP3 服务发送精心构造的超长 USER 命令，触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务崩溃或可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响安装 NAV2000 的 Windows 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，需升级至不受影响版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1004"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.250","remediation":"立即安装 Symantec 为 NAV2000 发布的 POProxy 安全补丁（文档 ID: 6206f660a1f2516a882568660082c930），或升级到 Norton AntiVirus 2001 及以上版本。如暂时无法更新，可禁用 POP3 邮件扫描功能以关闭 POProxy 服务，或在防火墙中限制对 TCP 110 端口的非信任来源访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://service1.symantec.com/SUPPORT/nav.nsf/df0a595864594c86852567ac0063608c/6206f660a1f2516a882568660082c930?OpenDocument&Highlight=0%2Cpoproxy","http://www.osvdb.org/6267","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/38970","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/39194","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1004.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1004","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1004.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1004.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1004.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4gvq-7hq9-g637/GHSA-4gvq-7hq9-g637.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1004.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000944.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0847.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0846","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0846.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0580","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表键权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE 注册表键存在权限配置不当漏洞，该键存储操作系统核心安全与配置信息，但默认权限设置过于宽松，导致未授权用户可读取甚至修改其中的系统关键项。攻击者可利用不当权限访问或篡改 HKLM 下安全策略、服务配置等关键数据，造成敏感信息泄露、权限提升乃至系统完全受控。该漏洞影响全系 Windows NT 操作系统，CVSS v2 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0580"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.357","remediation":"Windows NT 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2019/2022 或更高版本。如无法升级，需手动收紧注册表权限：运行 regedt32，展开 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE，右键选择「权限」，移除 Everyone 组的完全控制权，仅保留 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 的读取权限，并应用强制 ACL 继承到所有子项。同时部署组策略限制本地注册表远程访问。作为临时缓解，限制对受影响主机的网络访问并启用注册表审计日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0580","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0580.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0580.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-