绕过安全监控机制。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及早期版本，CVSS 评分 10.0（严重），属于安全审计绕过类漏洞。攻击条件为本地或远程拥有文件系统访问权限，利用方式为直接操作非关键文件/目录且不留痕迹。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0577"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.007","remediation":"tags\n- The content inside <value> will be used as the remediation field\n\nLet me craft a good Chinese remediation suggestion:\n- Upgrade to a modern Windows server version\n- Configure file audit policies properly\n- Provide specific steps and mitigation measures分析：CVE-1999-0577涉及Windows NT系统的文件审计策略未记录非关键文件/目录的成功/失败事件。根据漏洞描述，需要修复Windows NT的日志审计功能。\n\n<value>升级到Windows Server 2003 SP1或更高版本，使用本地安全策略配置“拒绝访问检查”和“成功/失败审计”策略，对于旧系统可通过修改注册表项[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Lsa]下的Audit基址来启用审计日志记录，如无法立即升级，建议通过组策略强制启用文件审计策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0577","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0577","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0577.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p3j3-4263-vqh3/GHSA-p3j3-4263-vqh3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0577.json","https://github.